title: President Donald J. Trump Signs H.R. 219 and H.R. 220 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Land & Agriculture	

Issued on:
July 20, 2018
On Friday, July 20, 2018, the President signed into law:H.R. 219, the “Swan Lake Hydroelectric Project Boundary Correction Act,” which directs a new land survey and land patent relating to the Swan Lake Hydroelectric Project near Ketchikan, Alaska; andH.R. 220, which authorizes the expansion of the Terror Lake Hydroelectric Project in Alaska.
